OL,6,FA disqualified driver fled the scene
OL,7,Fof a car crash in which his girlfriend
OL,8,Fwas fatally injured and later tried to
OL,9,Fblame her for the crash.
OL,11,FCameron Jones, 30, has been sentenced
OL,12,Fto 10 years in prison and disqualified
OL,13,Ffrom driving for 10 years for causing
OL,14,Fthe death of passenger Demi Mabbitt.
