OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FHe was driving an Audi S3 along the
OL,7,Fresidential area of Swansea Road in
OL,8,FMerthyr Tydfil on April 5 at motorway
OL,9,Fspeeds before it crashed into a wall,
OL,10,Fleaving 25-year-old passenger Demi
OL,11,FMabbitt, from Aberfan, lying injured
OL,12,Fin the road.
OL,14,FWitnesses at the scene reported
OL,15,Fhearing Jones say "I need to get the
OL,16,Fguy who was driving the car" and "my
OL,17,Fmissus just crashed the car".
OL,19,FMs Mabbitt died as a result of her
OL,20,Fextensive injuries a week later on 12
OL,21,FApril.
