OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FJones, from Merthyr Tydfil, fled the
OL,7,Fscene and avoided arrest for three
OL,8,Fweeks, with police launching a manhunt
OL,9,Fto try and find him.
OL,11,FHe eventually surrendered himself at a
OL,12,Fpolice station on 28 April.
OL,14,FHe answered no comment during a police
OL,15,Finterview, but admitted he was the
OL,16,Fdriver.
