OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FThe prosecution case included CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage showing the vehicle being
OL,8,Fdriven by Jones and him fleeing the
OL,9,Fscene, while DNA evidence from the car
OL,10,Fcorroborated Jones as being the driver.
OL,12,FJones had been significantly exceeding
OL,13,Fthe speed limit.
OL,15,FIt was thought that due to his
OL,16,Fexcessive speed, the wet road
OL,17,Fconditions and insufficient tread on
OL,18,Fthe rear tyres, the car aquaplaned and
OL,19,Fcrashed into a boundary wall.
