OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FAt a court hearing in May, he pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving; causing death by driving
OL,9,Fwhilst uninsured; causing death by
OL,10,Fdriving whilst disqualified; failing
OL,11,Fto stop after a road accident; and
OL,12,Ffailing to report it.
OL,14,FHe was jailed at Merthyr Tydfil Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Wednesday, 17 July.
