OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Debbie Hobrough, of
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police, said: "Demi
OL,8,FMabbitt lay dying on the side of the
OL,9,Froad when Jones callously fled from
OL,10,Fthe scene of the crash without trying
OL,11,Fto help her.
OL,13,F"The tragic manner of Demi's death has
OL,14,Fshaken the whole community.
OL,16,F"Cameron Jones' actions on April 5
OL,17,Fwere appalling and his attempts to
OL,18,Fescape justice ultimately failed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
