OL,6,F"Today's sentence will mean that Jones
OL,7,Fis behind bars and unable to cause
OL,8,Ffurther harm."
OL,10,FAfter sentencing, Demi's family said:
OL,11,F"Today has been another difficult day
OL,12,Fin the journey of our devastating loss.
OL,14,F"No sentence will ever be enough to
OL,15,Fbring justice for the death of our
OL,16,Fbeautiful girl Demi.
