OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,F"Demi was only 25 years old, she had
OL,7,Fher whole life ahead of her. She was
OL,8,Fthe kindest, most selfless person you
OL,9,Fcould meet. She had the biggest heart,
OL,10,Fthe most beautiful smile and a laugh
OL,11,Fmore infectious than any.
OL,13,F"Demi was her Mam's best friend, Dad's
OL,14,Ftwo eyes. Younger sister to Gemma, Ben
OL,15,Fand Jordan. Older sister to Callie and
OL,16,FKeisha but the boss of them all. Her
OL,17,Fniece and nephews were spoilt rotten
OL,18,Fand were her world. Nothing was ever
OL,19,Ftoo much trouble for her. Our family
OL,20,Fis broken.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
