OL,6,F"We would like to thank South Wales
OL,7,FPolice for their efforts and support
OL,8,Fthroughout. We would especially like
OL,9,Fto thank our family liaison officer PC
OL,10,FSaunders who has supported our family
OL,11,Fwith the upmost respect and compassion
OL,12,Fat the most difficult time of our
OL,13,Flives.
OL,15,F"We love you Dems, forever and always."
