OL,3,C'Callous' driver left girlfriend to
OL,4,Cdie in road after crashing car
OL,6,FJordan Jones, a senior crown
OL,7,Fprosecutor in CPS Cymru-Wales, said:
OL,8,F"This case highlights the severe
OL,9,Fconsequences of dangerous driving.
OL,10,FCameron Jones' actions have led to a
OL,11,Ftragic loss of life, and his attempts
OL,12,Fto evade responsibility only
OL,13,Fcompounded the grief of Demi Mabbit's
OL,14,Floved ones. Our thoughts remain with
OL,15,FDemi's family and friends."
